'''Brendon Baerg''' (born February 25, 1998; [[Whittier, California|Whittier]], [[California]]) is a child actor best known for playing "Logan Hughes" on the [[CBS]] [[sitcom]] ''[[Yes, Dear]]''. He voiced Thumper in ''[[Bambi II]]'' (released in [[2006 in film|2006]]).

